[
    {
        "text": "Let's get this out of the way.",
        "startTime": 755,
        "endTime": 1806,
        "slowStartTime": 1283,
        "slowEndTime": 2934
    },
    {
        "text": "Ancient Greece and Rome were really colorful.",
        "startTime": 2082,
        "endTime": 4148,
        "slowStartTime": 3273,
        "slowEndTime": 6447
    },
    {
        "text": "Their buildings were full of intricate frescoes and elaborate mosaics...",
        "startTime": 4650,
        "endTime": 8001,
        "slowStartTime": 7125,
        "slowEndTime": 12227
    },
    {
        "text": "...and covered with vibrantly painted statues...",
        "startTime": 8107,
        "endTime": 10293,
        "slowStartTime": 12311,
        "slowEndTime": 15664
    },
    {
        "text": "...of things like epic battles, glimmering gods, and pretty flowers.",
        "startTime": 10535,
        "endTime": 14397,
        "slowStartTime": 15952,
        "slowEndTime": 21820
    },
    {
        "text": "But today, most of us picture something more like this...",
        "startTime": 15072,
        "endTime": 17994,
        "slowStartTime": 22758,
        "slowEndTime": 27216
    },
    {
        "text": "...brilliant white marble as far as the eye can see.",
        "startTime": 18206,
        "endTime": 20719,
        "slowStartTime": 27459,
        "slowEndTime": 31304
    },
    {
        "text": "We're wrong.",
        "startTime": 21567,
        "endTime": 22113,
        "slowStartTime": 32500,
        "slowEndTime": 33394
    },
    {
        "text": "But, it's not our fault.",
        "startTime": 22371,
        "endTime": 23577,
        "slowStartTime": 33706,
        "slowEndTime": 35590
    },
    {
        "text": "It's Hollywood's fault.",
        "startTime": 23785,
        "endTime": 24577,
        "slowStartTime": 35827,
        "slowEndTime": 37091
    },
    {
        "text": "And our high school textbooks' fault.",
        "startTime": 24875,
        "endTime": 26589,
        "slowStartTime": 37463,
        "slowEndTime": 40108
    },
    {
        "text": "White marble became the norm.",
        "startTime": 27093,
        "endTime": 29144,
        "slowStartTime": 40790,
        "slowEndTime": 43941
    },
    {
        "text": "Along the way, art historians reinforced this bias.",
        "startTime": 30149,
        "endTime": 33317,
        "slowStartTime": 45374,
        "slowEndTime": 50200
    },
    {
        "text": "Namely this guy, Johann Joachim Winckelmann.",
        "startTime": 33742,
        "endTime": 36580,
        "slowStartTime": 50763,
        "slowEndTime": 55095
    },
    {
        "text": "He's sometimes known as the father of Art History.",
        "startTime": 36735,
        "endTime": 38817,
        "slowStartTime": 55253,
        "slowEndTime": 58450
    },
    {
        "text": "In the 18th century, he wrote a hugely influential book on ancient art.",
        "startTime": 39268,
        "endTime": 43397,
        "slowStartTime": 59052,
        "slowEndTime": 65321
    },
    {
        "text": "He went out of his way to ignore obvious evidence of colored marble,...",
        "startTime": 44205,
        "endTime": 47867,
        "slowStartTime": 66458,
        "slowEndTime": 72025
    },
    {
        "text": "...and there was a lot of it,...",
        "startTime": 48120,
        "endTime": 49601,
        "slowStartTime": 72330,
        "slowEndTime": 74627
    },
    {
        "text": "...especially after the rediscovery of the ancient Roman city of Pompeii in the 1700s.",
        "startTime": 49889,
        "endTime": 55171,
        "slowStartTime": 74984,
        "slowEndTime": 82981
    },
    {
        "text": "And one particular mural of an artist in the act of painting a sculpture.",
        "startTime": 55354,
        "endTime": 59200,
        "slowStartTime": 83181,
        "slowEndTime": 89025
    },
    {
        "text": "This colorful sculpture was also found in Pompeii.",
        "startTime": 60303,
        "endTime": 62568,
        "slowStartTime": 90604,
        "slowEndTime": 94077
    },
    {
        "text": "Winckelmann claimed it was too primitive to have been made by them.",
        "startTime": 62979,
        "endTime": 65961,
        "slowStartTime": 94619,
        "slowEndTime": 99167
    },
    {
        "text": "But, evidence wasn't just ignored.",
        "startTime": 67900,
        "endTime": 69747,
        "slowStartTime": 102000,
        "slowEndTime": 104846
    },
    {
        "text": "Some of it might have been destroyed.",
        "startTime": 69958,
        "endTime": 71497,
        "slowStartTime": 105087,
        "slowEndTime": 107471
    },
    {
        "text": "Luckily, art historians have since shifted to believe...",
        "startTime": 72032,
        "endTime": 74677,
        "slowStartTime": 108198,
        "slowEndTime": 112240
    },
    {
        "text": "...it's not about what people think looks better.",
        "startTime": 74758,
        "endTime": 76851,
        "slowStartTime": 112287,
        "slowEndTime": 115501
    },
    {
        "text": "It's about what's accurate.",
        "startTime": 77079,
        "endTime": 77923,
        "slowStartTime": 115769,
        "slowEndTime": 117110
    },
    {
        "text": "But, how did they get from this to this?",
        "startTime": 78582,
        "endTime": 81565,
        "slowStartTime": 118023,
        "slowEndTime": 122573
    },
    {
        "text": "Today, scientists can extract and test those tiny samples...",
        "startTime": 84178,
        "endTime": 87735,
        "slowStartTime": 126417,
        "slowEndTime": 131827
    },
    {
        "text": "...to determine the original pigments used.",
        "startTime": 87940,
        "endTime": 89800,
        "slowStartTime": 132060,
        "slowEndTime": 134925
    },
    {
        "text": "To the Greeks and the Romans, painting a sculpture made it complete.",
        "startTime": 90492,
        "endTime": 93769,
        "slowStartTime": 135888,
        "slowEndTime": 140878
    },
    {
        "text": "Color can make marble seem human or godlike.",
        "startTime": 94422,
        "endTime": 97929,
        "slowStartTime": 141783,
        "slowEndTime": 147119
    },
    {
        "text": "It infused them with drama and emotion.",
        "startTime": 98637,
        "endTime": 100739,
        "slowStartTime": 148105,
        "slowEndTime": 151333
    },
    {
        "text": "It brought history and mythology to life.",
        "startTime": 101289,
        "endTime": 103737,
        "slowStartTime": 152084,
        "slowEndTime": 155831
    },
    {
        "text": "And even though these reconstructions aren't perfect,...",
        "startTime": 104127,
        "endTime": 106951,
        "slowStartTime": 156340,
        "slowEndTime": 160652
    },
    {
        "text": "...seeing these statues in color...",
        "startTime": 107081,
        "endTime": 108677,
        "slowStartTime": 160771,
        "slowEndTime": 163241
    },
    {
        "text": "...can bring us a little closer...",
        "startTime": 108790,
        "endTime": 110302,
        "slowStartTime": 163335,
        "slowEndTime": 165678
    },
    {
        "text": "...to understanding what the ancient world might have looked like.",
        "startTime": 110433,
        "endTime": 113209,
        "slowStartTime": 165799,
        "slowEndTime": 170038
    }
]